      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "<p>The following cyclic structure is that of allose. Is this a furanose or pyranose form? Is it an <i>α</i> or a <i>β</i> anomer? Is it a <small style=\"font-variant: small-caps\">D</small> or an <small style=\"font-variant: small-caps\">L</small> sugar?</p>\n<img class=\"scaled-down-30\" src=\"https://exercises.openstax.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/proxy/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBb29aIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--55028d8c3b0ed924ef41e04f52fb82d312c21b08/OChem_25_EC_015.jpg\" alt=\"The Haworth projection of beta anomer of pyranose sugar named allose.\">",
